snippet.title: Hirocato - The Delivery Hero Trailer (Beta)
snippet.description: Hirocato is a fast-paced side-scroller where you play as a cat delivering food through tricky paths while discovering the hidden truths behind his world's downfall. The game is loaded with hard-to-beat levels, great music, hand-made pixel art, and an emotional story.
